### ====================================================
### PARTE 5: GET POR ID (200 Y 404)
### ====================================================

### 32. GET CPU por ID existente (200)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 33. GET CPU por ID inexistente (404)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/99999
Accept: application/json

###

### 34. GET GPU por ID existente (200)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/gpus/4
Accept: application/json

###

### 35. GET GPU por ID inexistente (404)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/gpus/99999
Accept: application/json

###

### 36. GET RAM por ID existente (200)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/rams/7
Accept: application/json

###

### 37. GET RAM por ID inexistente (404)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/rams/99999
Accept: application/json

###

### 38. GET Motherboard por ID existente (200)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/motherboards/10
Accept: application/json

###

### 39. GET Motherboard por ID inexistente (404)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/motherboards/99999
Accept: application/json

###

### 40. GET PSU por ID existente (200)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/psus/13
