### ====================================================
### PARTE 6: PUT (VALIDO E INVALIDO)
### ====================================================

### 42. PUT CPU valido (201 esperado por codelab)
PUT http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"brand": "AMD",
	"model": "Ryzen 7 7800X3D",
	"price": 1999000,
	"socket": "AM5",
	"cores": 8,
	"threads": 16,
	"tdp": 120
}

###

### 43. PUT CPU invalido (400, model vacio)
PUT http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"brand": "AMD",
	"model": "",
	"price": 1999000,
	"socket": "AM5",
	"cores": 8,
	"threads": 16,
	"tdp": 120
}

###

### ====================================================
### PARTE 7: DELETE (204)
### ====================================================

### 44. DELETE CPU existente (204)
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/2

###

### 45. DELETE GPU existente (204)
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/gpus/5

###

### 46. DELETE RAM existente (204)
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/rams/8

###

### 47. DELETE Motherboard existente (204)
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/motherboards/11

###

### 48. DELETE PSU existente (204)
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/psus/14

